Much rather know where i stand, then have no idea. When SoE said working as intended i knew it A) wasn't broken, or B) wasn't an exploit.<br />
<br />
Blizzard gives us so much schtick it's hard to tell what's what. One of the things that annoys me is, with EQ1 i knew where i stood with the Devs. They don't care what I think, will do what they want, and have no qualms about abusing me to make money. With EQ2 at the moment, they care what i think, will do changes based on my feedback, and have a very good upgrade schedule. With Blizzard they say they are listening, they say they are doing something to help me, but in actuality I have no idea what they are doing, nor when they plan to do it. It's stupid.<br />
<br />
